nd appearance of the event, which had been introduced in 1904 but not held in 1908 or 1912.\n\nEight nations competed.\n\n==Rosters==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-1-of-3}}\n;Belgium\n* [[L\u00e9on Tom]]\n* [[Robert Hennet]]\n* [[Marcel Cuypers]]\n* [[Fernand de Montigny]]\n* [[\u00c9mile De Schepper]]\n* [[Charles Crahay]]\n* [[Marcel Berr\u00e9]]\n* [[Charles Pape]]\n\n;Czechoslovakia\n* [[Josef Jav\u016frek]]\n* [[Anton\u00edn Mikala]]\n* [[Vil\u00e9m Tvrzsk\u00fd]]\n* [[Franti\u0161ek Dvo\u0159\u00e1k (fencer)|Franti\u0161ek Dvo\u0159\u00e1k]]\n\n;Denmark\n* [[Ivan Osiier]]\n* [[Georg Hegner]]\n* [[Ejnar Levison]]\n* [[Poul Rasmussen]]\n* [[Kay Schr\u00f8der]]\n{{col-2-of-3}}\n\n;France\n* [[Lionel Bony de Castellane]]\n* [[Gaston Amson]]\n* [[Philippe Cattiau]]\n* [[Roger Ducret]]\n* [[Andr\u00e9 Labatut]]\n* [[Georges Trombert]]\n* [[Lucien Gaudin]]\n* [[Marcel Perrot]]\n\n;Great Britain\n* [[Edgar Seligman]]\n* [[Roland Willoughby]]\n* [[Philip Doyne]]\n* [[Robert Montgomerie (fencer)|Robert Montgomerie]]\n* [[H. Evan James|Evan James]]\n* [[Cecil Kershaw]]\n\n{{col-3-of-3}}\n;Italy\n* [[Tommaso Costantino]]\n* [[Aldo Nadi]]\n* [[Nedo Nadi]]\n* [[Abelardo Olivier]]\n* [[Oreste Puliti]]\n* [[Pietro Speciale]]\n* [[Rodolfo Terlizzi]]\n* [[Baldo Baldi]]\n\n;Netherlands\n* [[Wouter Brouwer]]\n* [[F\u00e9lix Vigeveno]]\n* [[Salomon Zeldenrust]]\n* [[Adrianus de Jong|Arie de Jong]]\n* [[Jan van der Wiel]]\n\n;United States\n* [[Henry Breckinridge (fencer)|Henry Breckinridge]]\n* [[Francis Honeycutt]]\n* [[Arthur Lyon (fencer)|Arthur Lyon]]\n* [[Harold Rayner]]\n* [[Robert Sears]]\n\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Results==\n\n===Semifinals===\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=5| Pool A\n|-\n! Place || Team || Wins || Losses || Qual.\n|-\n| 1 ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|ITA|1920 Summer}} || 4 || 0 || '''Q'''\n|-\n| 2 ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|DEN|1920 Summer}} || 3 || 1 || '''Q'''\n|-\n| 3 ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|GBR|1920 Summer}} || 2 || 3 || '''Q'''\